Promotional poster in the style of a [film poster](/Film_poster)  

[Monaco: What's Yours Is Mine](/Monaco:_What%27s_Yours_Is_Mine) is a 2013 [stealth video game](/Stealth_video_game) developed by Pocketwatch Games in which players, [alone](/Single-player_video_game) or [cooperatively](/Cooperative_video_game), perform heists and robberies. Players choose from eight characters, each of whom has a unique and beneficial skill, such as the ability to change appearance or tunnel through walls. Monaco ’s single‑player story is told in four acts from perspectives of different characters. The cooperative mode lets up to four players play together in different locations.  

Lead developer [Andy Schatz](/Andy_Schatz) began developing Monaco while working for [TKO Software](/TKO_Software). He later founded his independent company Pocketwatch, where he continued development and planned to release it as an [Xbox Live Indie Game](/Xbox_Live_Indie_Games). While looking for [playtesters](/Playtest), Schatz met Andy Nguyen, who became a level designer, producer, and promoter for Monaco . Pocketwatch Games released the game in 2013 for [Windows](/Windows), [OS X](/OS_X), and [Linux](/Linux). [Majesco Entertainment](/Majesco_Entertainment) handled its [Xbox 360](/Xbox_360) release after [Microsoft Game Studios](/Microsoft_Game_Studios) twice rejected the game. A [Nintendo Switch](/Nintendo_Switch) version, Monaco: Complete Edition , was released in 2019 by [Humble Games](/Humble_Games).  

Monaco received positive reviews and won two awards at the 2010 [Independent Games Festival](/Independent_Games_Festival). Critics praised its cooperative modes but considered its single‑player gameplay inferior for lacking content. Frequently compared to [heist films](/Heist_film), reviewers praised Monaco ’s [art style](/Game_art_design) and how its [minimalist](/Minimalism) design suited its gameplay. [Austin Wintory](/Austin_Wintory)'s soundtrack also received praise. Pocketwatch announced a sequel, [Monaco 2](/Monaco_2) , in March 2022. ( [Full article...](/Monaco:_What%27s_Yours_Is_Mine) )  

