**Image 11** – Koster in 2017  

[Raphael "Raph" Koster](/Raph_Koster) (born September 7, 1971) is an American entrepreneur, [game designer](/Computer_game_designer), and author of [A Theory of Fun for Game Design](/A_Theory_of_Fun_for_Game_Design) . Koster is widely recognized for his work as the lead designer of [Ultima Online](/Ultima_Online) and the creative director behind [Star Wars Galaxies](/Star_Wars_Galaxies) . From 2006 until 2013 he worked as the founder and president of [Metaplace](/Metaplace) (previously operating as [Areae](/Areae) and acquired by social‑gaming company [Playdom](/Playdom) in 2010, which was in turn acquired by [Disney](/Disney)) producing a [Facebook game](/Facebook_game) platform. ( [Full article...](/Raph_Koster) )  

