[Todd Andrew Howard](/Todd_Howard) (born 1970) is an American [video‑game designer](/Video_game_designer), [director](/Creative_director), and [producer](/Video_game_producer). He serves as director and executive producer at [Bethesda Game Studios](/Bethesda_Game_Studios), where he has led the development of the [Fallout](/Fallout_(franchise)) and [The Elder Scrolls](/The_Elder_Scrolls) series. He was also the game director for Starfield . ( [Full article...](/Todd_Howard) )  

