Multiple companies, including [Klarna](/Klarna), [StubHub](/StubHub), [Nintendo](/Nintendo), and [Professional Sports Authenticator](/Professional_Sports_Authenticator), pause price‑sensitive business actions in the U.S. to evaluate the impact of the recent tariff announcements. ( The Wall Street Journal ) (IGN) ( The Verge )  

